    {
      "id": "E:note:row346921:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "The pt ia an unfortunate 80yo man with multiple medical problems who    initiall",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row346921#s1",
      "text": "The pt ia an unfortunate 80yo man with multiple medical problems who    initially presented to an osh on [**9-12**] with noted weakness and a    presumed aspiration pnx."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row346921:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "A head ct revealed a hemorrhagic cva at the    site of a known brain tumor.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row346921#s2",
      "text": "A head ct revealed a hemorrhagic cva at the    site of a known brain tumor."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row346921:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "He now has left sided hemiparesis and his    medical course at the osh has been ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row346921#s3",
      "text": "He now has left sided hemiparesis and his    medical course at the osh has been complicated by multiple pnxs and an    inability to wean from ventilatory support."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row346921:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "His care has been further    complicated by a h/o mds for which he is chronicall",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row346921#s4",
      "text": "His care has been further    complicated by a h/o mds for which he is chronically anemic and    thrombocytopenic."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row346921:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "The pt has required nearly daily transfusions to    maintain a plt count >50k an",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row346921#s5",
      "text": "The pt has required nearly daily transfusions to    maintain a plt count >50k and a hct >25."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row346921:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "He was transferred to [**Hospital1 54**]    last evening at his family request f",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row346921#s6",
      "text": "He was transferred to [**Hospital1 54**]    last evening at his family request for another neurosurigal opinion."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row346921:7",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "PMH: (in addition to the above) cad s/p cabg x4 06; afib now off    coumadin; bi",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row346921#s7",
      "text": "PMH: (in addition to the above) cad s/p cabg x4 06; afib now off    coumadin; bilat dvt s and pe s s/p filter placement; prostrate ca    ^chol; htn; copd; gout; hyperparathyroidism; peg placement    Allergies: univasc-> electrolyte abnormalities; celexa->    lightheadedness    Leukocytosis    Assessment:    Repeat wbc 25 which is c/w previous data."
    },
